<p><div class="left-margin" id="set-C"><h2>Story</h2></div></p>

<p>Master and Mashu get sent to an idol Singularity. Being an idol represents the strength here. Ms Crane tried to save the master, and mashu from a battle with a random idol character, but the attempt fails. E-chan being an idol to save the master, and mashu. Then, they go to the living of E-chan together.</p>

<p><img src="/img/fgo-waltz/a4.jpg" alt="Ms-Crane" /></p>
<div align="center">Ms Crane</div>

<p><img src="/img/fgo-waltz/a2.jpg" alt="E-chan" /></p>
<div align="center">E-chan</div>

<p>Then they hear the grail being available when they attend the competition of grail live. To obtain the invitation to the competition, they plan to challege the famous idol pair, with Medb and Tamamo cat.
<img src="/img/fgo-waltz/a1.jpg" alt="Medb" /></p>
<div align="center">Medb</div>
<p><img src="/img/fgo-waltz/a3.jpg" alt="Tamamo-Cat" /></p>
<div align="center">Tamamo Cat</div>

<p>E-chan asks Medb and Tamamo cat to join the journey. A team borns here named AxXxS.</p>

<p><img src="/img/fgo-waltz/b1.jpg" alt="AxXxS" />
<img src="/img/fgo-waltz/b2.jpg" alt="AxXxS" /></p>
<div align="center">Form a new idol team "AxXxS"</div>

<p>As the new team, they start finding the next targets. The new competitors are Ushiwakamaru, Altera, Jeanne, and Helena. This team behaves as a group of actresses, instead of singing. AxXxS persists their way to perform, instead of following the style of their opponents, and then win the contest.</p>

<p><img src="/img/fgo-waltz/a11.jpg" alt="Ushiwakamaru" /></p>
<div align="center">Ushiwakamaru</div>
<p><img src="/img/fgo-waltz/a12.jpg" alt="Altera" /></p>
<div align="center">Altera</div>
<p><img src="/img/fgo-waltz/a9.jpg" alt="Jeanne" /></p>
<div align="center">Jeanne</div>
<p><img src="/img/fgo-waltz/a10.jpg" alt="Helena" /></p>
<div align="center">Helena</div>

<p>There is a hotel and holiday resort. Players can meet Nobu in summer outfit(musician?) there. Nitocris and Hassan of Serenity are the competitors this time. On the way, Medb gets hurt this time, and she needs to spare the responsibilities of being a center. Mashu joins the group, and E-chan receives the training from Medb. With the effort of the existing members, they are able to win the competition.</p>

<p><img src="/img/fgo-waltz/a8.jpg" alt="Nobu" /></p>
<div align="center">Nobu (Summer outfit)</div>
<p><img src="/img/fgo-waltz/a17.jpg" alt="Nitocris" /></p>
<div align="center">Nitocris</div>
<p><img src="/img/fgo-waltz/a18.jpg" alt="Hassan-of-Serenity" /></p>
<div align="center">Hassan of Serenity</div>

<p>The team AxXxS is finally able to enter the final round! They engage to compete the strongest idol group, with the members of Euryale, Shuten-douji, and Nero. It is interesting to see their fans separation to different people, and the concert still go well.</p>

<p>The team AxXxS manages to get the victory in the grail live! However, something strange happens, when another Ms Crane appears. Master and Mashu return to the beginning of the event. They decide to find out Ms Crane for more clues. Ms Crane finds her restriction, and try to break it. Then her memory returns (roughly). However, Medb and Tamamo cat have no memory of the journey of AxXxS anymore.</p>

<p>E-chan tries to fight against the another Ms Crane, and get the holy grail. Players can know the background of “this” Ms Crane, wanting to give return to her previous master. Her master passes away, and no one knows the talent of her previous master, of being good in design. She designs to hold events along with idols, and let them dress good in stage. The Ms Crane with master has the goal to seek for an idol with good potential to win in the grail live, and everything gets reset after the winner comes out. When master knows her intention, she/he suggests to hold an excellent stage, with all idols in this event, to farewell Ms Crane.</p>

<p>The most important thing here is, the experience would never be useless. Although everything is going to disappear in the Singuarity, the experience would not fade out.</p>

<p><div class="left-margin" id="set-D"><h2>Last Words</h2></div></p>
<p>I really love the story in the event. Every character is being vivid and try hard to meet their goals. The story is written in good pace, and even have turning point. Ms Crane has the lovable personality, although she is being a villain in the story.</p>

<p>And the costume are cute !</p>

